headline: 1 Magnificent High Yield Stock Down 33% to Buy and Hold Forever
summary: Other investors are likely to see the market declines as an opportunity to get aggressive and buy, perhaps picking up an ultra-high-yield stock like AGNC Investment (NASDAQ: AGNC).  It's better to cut the middle and go with a different type of investment.  AGNC Investment's gargantuan yield could be a siren call to dividend investors who think they are picking up a stock that will provide them with reliable income for the rest of their lives.
